#: ../../source/tab5/keyboard.rst:2 4a7afd79e3634f23a636554223ddb936
msgid "Tab5 Keyboard"
msgstr "Tab5 Keyboard"

#: ../../source/tab5/keyboard.rst:8 edcf7d0e589f47c78b93bd1595dad021
msgid ""
"The `Keyboard` class controls the Tab5 keyboard controller over I2C. It "
"supports character input callbacks, raw key matrix events, keyboard mode "
"configuration, backlight brightness, RGB LED settings, and I2C address "
"management."
msgstr ""
"`Keyboard` 类通过 I2C 控制 Tab5 键盘控制器。它支持字符输入回调、原始按键矩阵事件、键盘模式配置、背光亮度、RGB LED 设置和 I2C 地址管理。"

